Titolo: Project X Zone 2

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: Project X Zone 2 is a crossover tactical role-playing game for the Nintendo 3DS developed by Monolith Soft and published by Bandai Namco Entertainment. Despite the game being the sequel to Project X Zone, the plot is an homage to the events of its spiritual predecessor, Namco Ã— Capcom, whilst retaining a standalone story. The game is a crossover between various franchises from Bandai Namco, Capcom, and Sega, with special guests from Nintendo. The game was released in Japan in November 2015, and worldwide in February 2016.

Genere: Tactical role-playing

